# asdf toolchain for emisar — `asdf install` from the repo root provisions the dev
# environment for all three languages, and this file is the single source of truth
# for the Erlang + Elixir pins: portal-ci.yml reads it via setup-beam (version-file
# + version-type: strict), and the portal Docker build derives its --build-arg
# toolchain from it — so CI and the release image always match dev, nothing to
# hand-sync. golang: the go.work + both go.mod floor is 1.26.3 (runner/ + mcp/),
# which the Go CI tracks via go-version-file by design (it builds against the
# minimum we support); 1.26.4 here is the latest compatible patch for local dev.
# Go has no asdf plugin by default — run `asdf plugin add golang` once, then install.
erlang 29.0.2
elixir 1.20.1-otp-29
golang 1.26.4
